---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout title="Employee Onboarding at CorpX">
  <section class="mt-16 text-center">
    <h1 class="text-4xl font-bold mb-8">Welcome to CorpX Onboarding</h1>
    <p class="text-lg text-gray-700 mb-12">
      Start strong. Start confused.
    </p>

    <div class="space-y-12 text-left max-w-4xl mx-auto">
      <div>
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-2">8:00 AM – Welcome Email (Maybe)</h2>
        <p>HR sends you a cheerful welcome email — or they forget. Attachments include PDFs nobody reads and broken links to mandatory compliance training.</p>
      </div>

      <div>
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-2">9:00 AM – Waiting for IT</h2>
        <p>Your laptop might arrive today! If it does, expect expired VPN credentials and security software that blocks half your tools.</p>
      </div>

      <div>
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-2">10:30 AM – Meet Your Manager (Briefly)</h2>
        <p>Fifteen minutes of vague enthusiasm followed by "We'll circle back on expectations."</p>
      </div>

      <div>
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-2">11:00 AM – Environment Setup Adventure</h2>
        <p>Follow outdated setup guides. Open six tickets for missing permissions. Wait.</p>
      </div>

      <div>
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-2">12:30 PM – Mandatory Culture Training</h2>
        <p>Watch a 40-minute video about collaboration featuring stock footage of high-fiving strangers.</p>
      </div>

      <div>
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-2">2:00 PM – First Real Assignment</h2>
        <p>Investigate a legacy system assigned two years ago. No documentation. No context. Good luck!</p>
      </div>

      <div>
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-2">3:30 PM – Team Meet & Greet</h2>
        <p>Join a muted Zoom call where someone named Chris says "Welcome!" before disappearing.</p>
      </div>

      <div>
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-2">4:30 PM – Corporate Slack Induction</h2>
        <p>Added to 37 channels instantly. Spend an hour decoding acronyms and locating the team you allegedly joined.</p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="text-center mt-16">
      <a href="/careers" class="bg-blue-900 text-white px-8 py-4 rounded-md text-lg font-bold hover:bg-blue-700 transition">
        Explore Open Roles
      </a>
    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>
